00:12:06,305 --> 00:12:09,350
We will take actions
in the lunar lander,

257
00:12:09,350 --> 00:12:11,165
so float around randomly,

258
00:12:11,165 --> 00:12:13,220
take some good actions,
take some bad actions.

259
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:15,770
It's okay either way.
But you get lots of

260
00:12:15,770 --> 00:12:19,070
these tuples of when
it was in some state,

261
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:20,930
you took some actually
gathering what R

262
00:12:20,930 --> 00:12:23,480
of S and you got to
some state s prime.

263
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:26,840
What we will do is store to

264
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:30,665
10,000 most recent
examples of these tuples.

265
00:12:30,665 --> 00:12:32,749
As you run this algorithm,

266
00:12:32,749 --> 00:12:36,500
you will see many steps
in the lunar lander,

267
00:12:36,500 --> 00:12:38,960
maybe hundreds of
