332
00:15:34,280 --> 00:15:37,265
Then the next model you
train will be even better.

333
00:15:37,265 --> 00:15:39,665
When you update Q equals Q new.

334
00:15:39,665 --> 00:15:41,270
Then for the next time you train

335
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:43,160
a model Q of s prime

336
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:45,605
a prime will be an
even better estimate.

337
00:15:45,605 --> 00:15:47,990
As you run this algorithm on

338
00:15:47,990 --> 00:15:50,030
every iteration, Q of s prime,

339
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:52,955
