341
00:15:55,054 --> 00:15:57,500
so that when you run the
algorithm long enough,

342
00:15:57,500 --> 00:16:00,290
this will actually become
a pretty good estimate

343
00:16:00,290 --> 00:16:03,770
of the true value of Q of s,

344
00:16:03,770 --> 00:16:07,280
a, so that you can
then use this to pick,

345
00:16:07,280 --> 00:16:09,845
