to learn the Q functions.

350
00:16:23,645 --> 00:16:28,640
Hence DQN or DQ using
a neural network.

351
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:31,865
If you use the algorithm
as I described it,

352
00:16:31,865 --> 00:16:33,470
